property.value: That ring over there is called a Nemeton.~It's an ancient ritual site that the elder guardians of this forest used to get around faster.

property.name: jsonFile
property.value: It looks like some sort of ritual circle. Better leave it alone.

property.name: jsonFile
property.value: If you head north, out of the Celenor Forest, it starts getting cold quickly...~Here, the trees are like a blanket over the whole area. It contains the warmth inside.

property.name: jsonFile
property.value: Welcome to Fyddnymed, the anima of the Celenor Forest, Sanctuary to all.

property.name: jsonFile
property.value: Hello, traveler. Have you come to pay homage to the forest guardians?~These statues are mere echoes of the human form of the Celenor Forest guardians.~Centuries ago, they made the ultimate sacrifice to protect us all.

property.name: jsonFile
property.value: The lake amidst Fyddnymed contains the most pristine water found in all of Myrinnia.~The water flows in from the mountains to the east and the mystical aura that shrouds the Celenor Forest grants it mysterious properties.~The extraordinary growth of trees in Fyddnymed are a direct result of its properties.

property.value: Fyddnymed is the capital city of the Celenorian elves.~Be sure to visit the city's canopy if you're looking to trade or craft things!
